node.text:
If there is one term that sums up what Maybach and Robbe & Berking have in common, it is surely "sophistication". 

Since their foundation, both manufactories have stood for tradition and innovation as well as for the highest quality standards “Handmade in Germany” with a maximum of individualization in order to continuously exceed the expectations of their customers. 

#Maybach #MercedesMaybach #MaybachLuxury #RobbeBerking

[Kraftstoffverbrauch kombiniert: 12,0–11,7 l/100 km | CO₂-Emissionen kombiniert: 273–266 g/km I mb4.me/DAT-Leitfaden | Mercedes-Maybach GLS 600 4MATIC]

node.text:
When an engine is brought to the body of a vehicle and brings it to life, this is also known as a wedding. It is a similar moment when a ship is brought to the water and is launched.

Sailing yachts and luxury vehicles therefore have a lot more in common than one might think at first glance. Their creation is a consummate interplay of craftsmanship, care in selecting the best materials, technical know how, and a lot of time and pure passion. 

#Maybach #MaybachLuxury #MercedesMaybach #RobbeBerking 

[Kraftstoffverbrauch kombiniert: 14,1–13,3 l/100 km | CO₂-Emissionen kombiniert: 322–305 g/km I mb4.me/DAT-Leitfaden | Mercedes-Maybach S 680 4MATIC]

node.text:
MAYBACH Icons of Luxury complements the world of cars with a range of high quality accessories for an all-encompassing lifestyle experience. 

An impressive example of this are the @maybacheyewear sunglasses THE KING, whose handcrafted temples made of fine precious wood or genuine natural horn feature an open décor inspired by the dynamic lines of the centre console. 

#Maybach #MaybachLuxury #MaybachEyewear #MercedesMaybach #GLS

node.text:
Mercedes-Maybach embodies sophisticated luxury through its unique combination of passion and exquisite craftsmanship with state-of-the-art technology. The result is a brand that stands for a truly holistic luxury experience: one that celebrates creativity and goes beyond the product itself thanks to its compelling opportunities for individualisation and timeless elegance in exclusive materials. 

The Mercedes-Maybach GLS embodies these aspirations and brings a clear enrichment in the luxury SUV segment.

#Maybach #MercedesMaybach #GLS #MaybachLuxury

[Kraftstoffverbrauch kombiniert: 12,0–11,7 l/100 km | CO₂-Emissionen kombiniert: 273–266 g/km I mb4.me/DAT-Leitfaden | Mercedes-Maybach GLS 600 4MATIC]

node.text:
The roots of the MAYBACH brand go back well over a hundred years, when Wilhelm Maybach laid the cornerstone for a high-end automobile brand which quickly became a legend. For decades, MAYBACH has symbolized the most exacting demands on quality and luxury. 

#Maybach #MercedesMaybach #MaybachLuxury #MaybachMonday
